  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project relates to the Africa Climate Change Resilience Alliance programme. The ACCRA programme aims to increase the use of evidence by governments and other development and humanitarian actors in developing and implementing policies and interventions that improve poor people&apos;s resilience to climate change. The programme is implemented through a Consortium which includes ODI, Save the Children, World Vision and Care International. This project covers the grants made by Oxfam for the Consortium Members activities.</narrative>
